Added channel to WifiAccessPoint geolocation class

Added channel to WifiAccessPoint geolocation class

Some geolocation providers also accept wifi channel number
to perfom the geolocation more precisely. So protocols can
supply this additional information now.

Set Content Type in http header of geolocation request

Google geolocation API does not work correctly if
"Content-Type:application/json" is not present in http header.

Reset additional parameters of GPS position after geolocation

When geolocation found a lat/lon from LBS/WIFI, only lat/lon and
accuracy are updated.
If protocol has copied "last" position to "Position" class before
issuing the geolocation, then all other parameters of GPS position
will be invalid (from "last" position).
So this fix reset to 0 the altitude, speed, course and rssi.
